2. Interpretation
In this Act, unless the context otherwise requires—
"company" includes—
( a ) any association incorporated or registered under any law in force in Botswana;
( b ) any association which is incorporated or registered outside Botswana but carries on business or has an office or place of business in Botswana;
( c ) any body corporate established and incorporated by any law in force in Botswana or by any law in force in any country outside Botswana;
( d ) any international organisation of which Botswana is a member;
"financial year" means any period of 12 months ending on the 31st day of March;
